SELECT p.influencer_id, i.influencer_name, i.influencer_followers, COUNT(c.contract_id) AS contract_count FROM Partnerships p JOIN Influencers i ON p.influencer_id = i.influencer_id LEFT JOIN Contracts c ON p.partnership_id = c.partnership_id GROUP BY p.influencer_id, i.influencer_name, i.influencer_followers ORDER BY contract_count DESC;

SELECT c.contract_date, c.contract_value, c.payment_terms, d.deliverable_description, d.deliverable_due_date, d.status FROM Contracts c JOIN Deliverables d ON c.contract_id = d.contract_id WHERE c.contract_value > 1000 AND d.status = 'pending' ORDER BY c.contract_date ASC;

SELECT i.influencer_name, i.influencer_email, COUNT(p.partnership_id) AS partnership_count FROM Influencers i LEFT JOIN Partnerships p ON i.influencer_id = p.influencer_id GROUP BY i.influencer_name, i.influencer_email ORDER BY partnership_count DESC;

SELECT i.influencer_name, i.influencer_followers, d.deliverable_description, d.deliverable_due_date FROM Influencers i JOIN Partnerships p ON i.influencer_id = p.influencer_id JOIN Contracts c ON p.partnership_id = c.partnership_id JOIN Deliverables d ON c.contract_id = d.contract_id WHERE i.influencer_followers > 100000 ORDER BY i.influencer_followers DESC, d.deliverable_due_date ASC;
